#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.nan_to_num.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.nan\\_to\\_num"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num:1 of
msgid "Replace nan with zero and inf with large finite numbers."
msgstr "将 nan 替换为零，将 inf 替换为大的有限数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num:3 of
msgid ""
"If `x` is inexact, NaN is replaced by zero, and infinity and -infinity "
"replaced by the respectively largest and most negative finite floating "
"point values representable by ``x.dtype``."
msgstr ""
"如果 `x` 是不精确的，则 NaN 被替换为零，正负无穷大分别被替换为 ``x.dtype`"
"` 所能表示的最大和最小的有限浮点数值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num:7 of
msgid ""
"For complex dtypes, the above is applied to each of the real and "
"imaginary components of `x` separately."
msgstr "对于复数类型，上述操作会分别应用于 `x` 的实部和虚部。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num:10 of
msgid "If `x` is not inexact, then no replacements are made."
msgstr "如果 `x` 不是不精确类型，则不做任何替换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num:12 of
msgid "Input data."
msgstr "输入数据。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num:14 of
msgid ""
"Whether to create a copy of `x` (True) or to replace values in-place "
"(False). The in-place operation only occurs if casting to an array does "
"not require a copy. Default is True."
msgstr ""
"是否创建 `x` 的副本 (True) 或原地替换值 (False)。仅当转换为数组不需要复制"
"时才会进行原地操作。默认为 True。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num:20 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- `x`, with the non-finite values replaced. If `copy` is False, "
"this may be `x` itself."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 替换掉非有限值后的 `x`。如果 `copy` 为 False，则可能就是 `x` "
"本身。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num:26 of
msgid ":py:obj:`isinf`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num:27 of
msgid "Shows which elements are positive or negative infinity."
msgstr "显示哪些元素是正无穷或负无穷。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`isneginf`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num:30 of
msgid "Shows which elements are negative infinity."
msgstr "显示哪些元素是负无穷。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num:32 of
msgid ":py:obj:`isposinf`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num:33 of
msgid "Shows which elements are positive infinity."
msgstr "显示哪些元素是正无穷。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num:35 of
msgid ":py:obj:`isnan`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num:36 of
msgid "Shows which elements are Not a Number (NaN)."
msgstr "显示哪些元素是 NaN（非数字）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num:38 of
msgid ":py:obj:`isfinite`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num:39 of
msgid "Shows which elements are finite (not NaN, not infinity)"
msgstr "显示哪些元素是有限的（不是 NaN，也不是无穷大）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num:42 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.nan_to_num.nan_to_num:43 of
msgid ""
"MaxFrame uses the IEEE Standard for Binary Floating-Point for Arithmetic "
"(IEEE 754). This means that Not a Number is not equivalent to infinity."
msgstr ""
"MaxFrame 使用 IEEE 二进制浮点数算术标准 (IEEE 754)。这意味着 NaN（非数字"
"）与无穷大并不等价。"

